{"tid":1815222,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【討論】可唔可以再黎一次黎明行動？","createTime":"2020-01-07T10:57:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T15:53:34.000Z","uid":204163,"like":35,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"076a7dcb769c0fca14c3ae22ce2631e9bb8a2b42","tid":1815222,"uid":204163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T10:57:57.000Z","msg":"黎明行動的效力之大，相信唔洗多講<br />\n完全係港共的春袋<br />\n頭個星期直頭令成個香港癱瘓半日經濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於點解唔再有黎明行動<br />\n連登內風向有<span style=\"color: red;\">三</span>：<br />\n<br />\n1.工會籌備緊，唔好<span style=\"color: gold;\">強罷工</span><br />\n2.無左中大同理大塞幹道，<span style=\"color: gold;\">好難成事</span><br />\n3.狗<span style=\"color: gold;\">玩熟左</span>，容易比狗咬<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n作為o個兩個星期都有早睡早起<br />\n又去過中大參觀的良好市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我覺得呢三個都唔係問題<br />\n第一，根本黎明行動同籌組工會係兩件事，一條勇武線，一條和理非線，黎明行動唔會影響到工會的進度。相反，我認為更可以提高淺黃加入工會的動力，因為佢地希望用一種更<span style=\"color: gold;\">「和平」</span>的方式抗爭。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第二，全香港並唔係得紅隧同吐露港公路，點會因為咁就唔得？或者，我換個方式問，如果黎明行動<span style=\"color: gold;\">係正中環搞</span>，又會有幾大影響力呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第三，呢個我無咩好講，除左手足自己小心d，我覺得最大的問題係第一個星期之後開始<span style=\"color: gold;\">唔夠人</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好快就新年啦，唔知市民可唔可以提早放年假，<span style=\"color: red;\">初一至初三一齊和你shop</span>呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n恭喜發財，新年快樂<br />\n香港獨立，唯一出路"},{"pid":"d7d515ae8ce6e69fd8e9d839810cae85087a95e4","tid":1815222,"uid":204163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T10:58:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e4046103e4e3cec2db968ca8db89945e473d0203","tid":1815222,"uid":204163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T10:59:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61442b11d9fcd290e4007cff867ab4a7f76d09ad","tid":1815222,"uid":204163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T10:59:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cecfb2437c418950b3636d015a7f120cdceb616e","tid":1815222,"uid":13420,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T11:00:47.000Z","msg":"香港小隊正式宣布退出中共"},{"pid":"85dfcd5b505fe5c826b372caeb870d8d59876a15","tid":1815222,"uid":223643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T11:00:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b8e8a11bc87e44e1ae18652bfa52a7fdbba78d9","tid":1815222,"uid":69334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T11:01:13.000Z","msg":"支持新年商場和你防疫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-----------<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港獨立   唯一出路</span></strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n新症正名：<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>中國肺炎</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13adad915ffffe1c513031000eb9cc389b612d13","tid":1815222,"uid":223643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T11:01:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkg