e":"2020-01-07T11:18:38.000Z","msg":"我都好認同<br />\n如果真係做到有組織性的話<br />\n我會事先係公海大大聲講幾個地方，例如十個咁啦<br />\n等d狗分散人手部署<br />\n然後自己小隊就只係去其中一個地方<br />\n甚至以外的地方<br />\n等d狗疲於奔命<br />\n實則虛之，虛則實之<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但呢招最大的風險係<br />\n有機會fake 到自己人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以<span style=\"color: red;\">有組織</span>係最大的重點"},{"pid":"53d43ef9cf6ce1b6b4c97a0ff8a2cd1e31c13bdb","tid":1815222,"uid":204163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ef4d3161fafee9e445c2842b1575dcdc34a8695","tid":1815222,"uid":296607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T11:18:22.000Z","msg":"第一日都唔夠人啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T11:20:06.000Z","msg":"點會，你可以睇返果日d新聞<br />\n五毛就請上一頁"},{"pid":"9e135fd7685d51f8736e583054960de51896ea70","tid":1815222,"uid":204163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T11:20:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cb343431a4dce42c8c7289ac3940554468d4c08","tid":1815222,"uid":204163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T11:32:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"284d4a3e7a84ed29ed5e1c72068e055760150b06","tid":1815222,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T11:32:34.000Z","msg":"但驚俾狗咬<br />\n一推垃圾筒就俾狗㩒低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地要用靠人數唔靠勇先有得玩"},{"pid":"1880b0670b7b8534369262b8679a6be04ec7ff0b","tid":1815222,"uid":204163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T11:32:36.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86204fd7610d117cd02350f1618eda9eddbd